*Class-Spiffy-0.150.0-r1 (26 Aug 2014)

  26 Aug 2014; Ian Stakenvicius (_AxS_) <axs@gentoo.org>
  +Class-Spiffy-0.150.0-r1.ebuild, -Class-Spiffy-0.150.0.ebuild:
  bumped EAPI to 5; committed directly to stable as no other changes present and
  revbump helps stable systems to keep from dieing on perl-5.18 upgrade

  24 Oct 2012; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> Class-Spiffy-0.150.0.ebuild:
  Add ~amd64, wrt bug #439320

  24 Jun 2012; Torsten Veller <tove@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Update CPAN upstream info

  04 Sep 2011; Torsten Veller <tove@gentoo.org> -Class-Spiffy-0.15.ebuild:
  Cleanup

  03 Sep 2011; Torsten Veller <tove@gentoo.org> Class-Spiffy-0.150.0.ebuild:
  Merge stable keywords from former version scheme ebuild

